                  <div class="update-feed-item"><span class="update-time">6/22 09:20-09:31 BJT</span> Serenity 把 NAV 折价框架扩展到<b>台资+大陆子公司</b>——WUS TW（8292，楠梓电）持有 WUS Kunshan（沪士电子 002463）11.4%；按 42.04 亿人民币口径计算，该持股约值 4.79 亿元人民币。是否形成母公司折价仍需结合总股本、汇率、其他资产与负债复核；6/22 另补充 Palliser 入股 Ajinomoto 后 ABF 提价案例。</div>
                  <div class="update-feed-item"><span class="update-time">6/20 12:01 BJT</span> Serenity 拆解韩国 holding co 折价：Daeduck（353200，底层资产~3.8x MC，FC-BGA+MLB）、DB（~3.7x DB HiTek，Foundry）、Hyosung（~3.6x，变压器）</div>
                  <div class="update-feed-item"><span class="update-time">6/20 11:52 BJT</span> Priortech 持有 $CAMT 21%（~1.35x MC），NAV 折价框架从日韩扩散至以色列封测设备。</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Article list -->
      <div class="section-divider"><h2>📌 最新推文追踪</h2></div>
      {filtered.length > 0 ? (
        <ul>
          {filtered.map((post) => (
            <li>
              <a class="post-card" href={getPostUrl(post)}>
                {post.data.heroImage && <Image width={720} height={360} src={post.data.heroImage} alt="" />}
                <div>
                  <span class="pill pill-red">白发股神</span>
                  <h2 class="title">{post.data.title}</h2>
                </div>
                <p class="date">更新：<FormattedDate date={post.data.updatedDate ?? post.data.pubDate} showTime={true} /></p>
              </a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      ) : (
        <div class="empty">暂无推文。</div>
      )}
    </main>
    <Footer />
    <script is:inline>
      (() => {
        const visibleLimit = 5;
        document.querySelectorAll('.update-feed').forEach((feed) => {
          const items = [...feed.querySelectorAll(':scope > .update-feed-item')];
          if (items.length <= visibleLimit) return;

          const details = document.createElement('details');
          details.className = 'update-history';
          const summary = document.createElement('summary');
          summary.textContent = `历史动态（${items.length - visibleLimit} 条）`;
          const body = document.createElement('div');
          body.className = 'update-history-body';
          items.slice(visibleLimit).forEach((item) => body.append(item));
          details.append(summary, body);
          feed.append(details);
        });
      })();
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
